Class InodePathPair

  • java.lang.Object
    • alluxio.collections.Pair<LockedInodePath,LockedInodePath>
      • alluxio.master.file.meta.InodePathPair
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AutoCloseable

    @ThreadSafe
public final class InodePathPair
extends Pair<LockedInodePath,LockedInodePath>
implements AutoCloseable
    This class represents a pair of LockedInodePaths. This is threadsafe, since the elements cannot set once the pair is constructed.
